      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "A pretty charity party has been\nplanned by two charming hostesses,\nMrs. Valentine w. Brasch and Mrs.\nw. G.. Hall, to be given Thursday\nafternoon at the home of the former\non Sixth avenue.\n\n\nThe affair will be given as bene-\nfit for the Woman's club day nur-\nsery. Tables will be arranged to\naccommodate about 1875 guests."
